Bluetooth problem solving (win11)

Steps

After configing HC-05, if you cannot find it from bluetooth connection, Please check for the below setup:
  1. 1.
    Open Settings, go to Bluetooth & devices
  1. 2.
    Go to View more devices
  1. 3.
    You can see a Bluetooth devices discovery, the default setting of this item is Default, which is limiting you to find HC-05. Please change it to Advanced.
